  <h2 class="section-heading" id="sharing-conversations" data-jump-label="Sharing Conversations">Sharing Conversations</h2>
  <p class="section-description">Claude conversations can be shared with teammates — useful for showing your work, collaborating on a project, or sharing a useful prompt pattern you've discovered.</p>

  <!-- ── Why Share? ──────────────────────────────── -->
  <h2 class="section-heading" id="why-share" data-jump-label="Why Share?">Why Share?</h2>
  <ul class="feature-list">
    <li>Collaborate with teammates on AI-assisted work</li>
    <li>Hand off context when you're OOO</li>
    <li>Save valuable exchanges for future reference</li>
  </ul>

  <!-- ── How to Share ────────────────────────────── -->
  <h2 class="section-heading" id="how-to-share" data-jump-label="How to Share">How to Share</h2>
  <ol class="steps-list">
